AlertMe.tv
http://github.com/merbjedi/alertme_tv

See it live: http://alertme.tv

This theme depends on the FolioBlogger template which you'll need to buy a license for:
http://themeforest.net/item/folio-blogger/35546?ref=jcnetdev

You'll also need a TVDB api key: http://thetvdb.com

Any questions, please create an issue on GitHub issue tracker, or update the wiki.

Don't forget to run "thor merb:gem:redeploy" to compile all the gem dependencies. You must have Thor 0.9.9 installed for this to work (0.11 doesnt work).
